Class LynxMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.hardware.lynx.commands.LynxMessage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LynxAck, LynxNack, LynxRespondable

    public abstract class LynxMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    LynxMessage is the root base class from which all lynx messaging related classes derive.
